 fundamental understanding of MHPs; knowledge that could be coined\nto improve performance in future optoelectronic devices based on this promising\nclass of semiconductors.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 11 May 2023 17:57:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-12"}
