. Consequently, our results substantiate that the CIV/CIII]\nratio can be used as an indirect tracer of $f_{\\rm{esc}}$, providing a\npromising tool for identification of ionising sources among star-forming\ngalaxies in the epoch of reionisation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 11 May 2023 18:00:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-15"}
