l hundred Myr. As the amplitude of the\nvertical oscillation increases, the time spent in the galactic plane, where\nmost GMCs are distributed, decreases, and the rate of an increase in the\nheating and migration slows down.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 11 May 2023 18:00:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 25 May 2023 04:15:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-06-07"}
