 that the\ndata is in error. On the other hand, the model may not be accurately capturing\npressure attenuation through an under-fluidized region in the back of the bed.\nWithout the possibility additional experiments to test the validity of the\ndata, this work is simply being reported as is without being able to indicate\nwhich, either the simulation or the experiment, is more correct.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 11 May 2023 20:22:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-15"}
