ola according to time difference of\narrival and the user's off-grid location can be obtained by using the proposed\nPGD algorithm. Simulation results demonstrate the superiority of the two\nproposed localization schemes and the proposed CE scheme over state-of-the-art\nbaseline approaches.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 12 May 2023 00:49:31 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 23 May 2023 09:15:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-24"}
