ation\nerrors must remain well within 5\\% to retain good precision determination of\nthe parameters $\\sin^2\\theta_{23}$ and $\\Delta m^2_{32}$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 12 May 2023 07:43:41 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 15 May 2023 11:08:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-16"}
