\\ell_2(\\kappa)$ we construct a\ndiscrete subgroup $H$ which is a complete Banakh space of cardinality\n$|H|=\\max\\{\\kappa,\\omega\\}$, and a dense $\\mathbb Q$-linear subspace $L$ in\n$\\ell_2(\\kappa)$ such that $L$ is a Banakh space with $d[L^2]=\\mathbb R_+$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 12 May 2023 10:05:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-15"}
