grated spectra\ncan already provide reliable classifications of many systems. Finally, we\nsummarize the 14 confirmed dual AGNs at z>0.5 selected by the GMP technique,\nand compare this sample with other such systems from the literature, concluding\nthat GMP can provide a large number of confirmed dual AGNs at separations below\n7 kpc.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 12 May 2023 11:48:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-15"}
