 rather\nthan detailed microscopic behavior. Fine-tuned equation of state models will\nlikely remain unconstrained in the near future.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 12 May 2023 12:27:24 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 8 Jun 2023 13:17:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-06-09"}
